    "78087716": {
      "title": "Search for sterile neutrinos in MINOS and MINOS+ using a two-detector fit",
      "abstract": "A search for mixing between active neutrinos and light sterile neutrinos has been performed by looking for muon neutrino disappearance in two detectors at baselines of 1.04 and 735 km, using a combined MINOS and MINOS+ exposure of ::: 16.36 ::: \u00d7 ::: 10 ::: 20 ::: protons on target. A simultaneous fit to the charged-current muon neutrino and neutral-current neutrino energy spectra in the two detectors yields no evidence for sterile neutrino mixing using a ::: 3 ::: + ::: 1 ::: model. The most stringent limit to date is set on the mixing parameter ::: sin ::: 2 ::: \u03b8 ::: 24 ::: for most values of the sterile neutrino mass splitting ::: \u0394 ::: m ::: 2 ::: 41 ::: > ::: 10 ::: \u2212 ::: 4 ::: ::: ::: eV ::: 2 ::: ."
    }
